# MechvibesDX

Desktop app that plays mechanical keyboard/mouse sounds on input events. Built with **Rust** + **Dioxus 0.7** (React-like desktop UI framework). Styled with **Tailwind CSS 4** + **DaisyUI**.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Language | Rust (edition 2024) |
| UI | Dioxus 0.7.2 (desktop feature) |
| Audio | rodio, cpal, symphonia (MP3/WAV/OGG/AAC) |
| Input capture | rdev (global), device_query (focused window), evdev (Linux) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 4 + DaisyUI themes |
| System tray | tray-icon crate |
| IPC | crossbeam-channel (input events), std::sync::mpsc (window actions) |

